                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7924" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1236</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2201 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">3000亿蒸发：“酱茅”背后的“忧”与“优”</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">300 billion vaporization:The worries and advantages behind the leader of the soy sauce industry</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">何忠，李恩临，赵甜甜，吴心如，曾美麒</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">福建农林大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">佛山市海天调味食品股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">食品工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">12 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">海天味业；经营困境；财务报表分析</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Haitian Taste Industry;Business difficulties;Financial statement analysis</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">随着我国居民生活水平的提高，消费者饮食口味趋向于多样化，调味品种类日益增多，加之疫情对实业经济的冲击，调味品行业的市场竞争愈发激烈。海天味业作为调味品行业的龙头企业也面临着前所未有的经营困境。在此背景下，本案例结合财务报表分析相关理论，以海天“双标”事件的爆发为引，讲述了海天味业“昔日辉煌-如今经营状况忧虑重重-进行海天精调-尽显龙头之优”的故事。通过本案例的学习，引导学习者深入理解财务报表相关数据背后所表现的企业发展状况，再结合海天味业的实际，共同研究和探讨当企业经营环境发生变化时，企业应该如何从财报中发现端倪，并及时采取手段调控避害，有效应对潜在风险，以促使企业在多重压力下保持稳步的发展。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">With the improvement of the living standards of Chinese residents, consumers&#39; dietary tastes tend to be diversified, the variety of seasonings is increasing, and the impact of the epidemic on the industrial economy, the market competition in the condiment industry has become more and more fierce. As a leading enterprise in the condiment industry, Haitian flavor Industry is also facing unprecedented operational difficulties.In this context, this case combined with the analysis of financial statements related theories, with the outbreak of the Haitian &quot;double standard&quot; incident as a reference, tells the story of the Haitian flavor industry &quot;the past glory - now the business situation is very worried - the Haitian fine adjustment - full of the leading advantages&quot;. Through the study of this case, learners will be guided to have a deep understanding of the development status of enterprises reflected in the relevant data of financial statements, and combined with the actual situation of Haitian flavor industry, jointly study and discuss how enterprises should find clues from financial statements when the business environment of enterprises changes, take timely measures to regulate and avoid harm, and effectively deal with potential risks. In order to promote the enterprise to maintain steady development under multiple pressures.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《高级财务管理理论与实践》、《财务报表分析》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">利益相关者的要求；财务报表分析；敏感性分析法；波特五力模型</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-12</td>
                            </tr>
